      "name": "Image with Text V2",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "<p>Why Rejuvia works <em>3x faster and stronger </em>than sleeping pills and gummies</p>",
        "description": "<p>Most sleep supplements lose up to 80% of their ingredients in your stomach. You're essentially paying for filler and a placebo effect.</p><p>Rejuvia is different. As a sublingual spray, it absorbs directly under your tongue and into your bloodstream in minutes — bypassing your digestive system entirely. Nothing wasted. Nothing lost.</p><p>And with 13 all-natural ingredients working together in a triple-action sleep formula, you're not just falling asleep faster — you're getting the deep, restorative sleep your body actually needs.</p><p>No dependency. No morning fog. Just the sleep you've been missing.</p>",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/REJUVIA_2.0_WEB_Section3_Graph.webp"
      }
    },
